.\" Generated by help2man for steam-game-idler
.TH STEAM-GAME-IDLER 1 "June 2026" "Steam Game Idler 5.0.15" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
steam-game-idler \- Idle Steam games and farm trading cards
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B steam-game-idler
[\fIOPTION\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Steam Game Idler is a tool to idle Steam games for playtime, farm trading cards,
and unlock achievements automatically.
.PP
Features:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Idle any game in your Steam library
.IP \(bu 2
Farm trading cards automatically
.IP \(bu 2
Unlock achievements and statistics
.IP \(bu 2
Auto-redeem free games
.IP \(bu 2
Discord Rich Presence integration
.IP \(bu 2
System tray support
.IP \(bu 2
Start minimized / at login
.RE
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
Show help message and exit.
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Show version information and exit.
.TP
\fB\-\-portable\fR
Run in portable mode (stores data next to the executable).
.TP
\fB\-\-clear-cache\fR
Clear all cache files on startup.
.TP
\fB\-\-reset-settings\fR
Reset all settings to defaults on startup.
.SH FILES
.TP
\fI~/.local/share/steam-game-idler/\fR
User data directory (settings, logs, credentials).
.TP
\fI~/.local/share/steam-game-idler/cache/\fR
Cache directory (game data, trading cards, custom lists).
.TP
\fI~/.config/autostart/steam-game-idler.desktop\fR
Autostart desktop entry (created when "Run at startup" is enabled).
.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
.TP
\fBKEY\fR, \fBSTEAM_API_KEY\fR
Steam Web API key for API-dependent features.
.TP
\fBSGI_STEAM_UTILITY_PATH\fR
Custom path to SteamUtility.Cli binary.
.TP
\fBSGI_DISABLE_DEV_TRAY\fR
Set to 1 to disable system tray in development mode on Linux.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR steam (1)
.PP
